ji\" /> 用下腦"},{"pid":"6c063da12826f616af55b10fc759d856fcb65515","tid":530674,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b7b974bb4d5df79abd54f987e663af14716a71","tid":530674,"uid":21634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1cf9932b36e0b489ea89780fd5f850d452bb20b","tid":530674,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"702d6cc08d5db5d2a3a965e1d2a2e3f8045bce4b","tid":530674,"uid":7318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:25:50.000Z","msg":"三重彩四重彩<br />\n係要買中指定位置喎"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"三四重彩本身要順序先會贏，但買複式可以唔使順序，咁又點計"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"你買複式就係買哂咁多個組合，點樣順序買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ne.g. 三重彩複式 1+2+3 $10注 total$60<br />\n包含6條飛：<br />\n1+2+3<br />\n1+3+2<br />\n2+1+3<br />\n2+3+1<br />\n3+1+2<br />\n3+2+1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T10:56:08.000Z","msg":"幫你解釋埋啦，當賽果真係跑1+2+3，你其他5注都唔中，因為個順序唔啱。（三重彩要跟順序）<br />\n<br />\n六合彩親完全無呢個問題，因為無論攪珠順序係123456定 654321都好，你買中1-6就中頭獎。<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下，6合彩如果要跟順序中嘅，應該幾百年先有一個中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}